%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
POSTDOCTORAL POSITION
LIFO, Universit=C3=A9 d'Orl=C3=A9ans, France
%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%

+ Title: Data Science Queries: Language and Algorithms
+ Founding: Regional project DOING (APR-IA, Region Centre Val de Loire)
+ Starting: 01/02/2023 (approximative)
+ Length: 12 months.
+ Research laboratory:=C2=A0 LIFO (https://www.univ-orleans.fr/lifo/?lang=
=3Den)
(PAMDA team), Universit=C3=A9 d'Orl=C3=A9ans, France
+ Collaboration with the following laboratories:
---- LIFAT (https://lifat.univ-tours.fr/) and
---- LIRIS (https://liris.cnrs.fr/
+ Salarie : 2000=E2=82=AC net.
