involves knowledge in the domain of databases and of machine learning.=20
Skills on at least ONE of these areas are required. The candidate should=20
also be motivated to invest in the complementary field.=C2=A0 A good Engl=
ish=20
level is also required.

French is not mandatory for candidates with a very good level of English=20
and willing to learn=C2=A0 French for daily life in France.

The research work is conducted at=C2=A0 the Laboratoire d'Informatique=20
Fondamentale d'Orl=C3=A9ans (LIFO), in France. The postdoctoral fellow sh=
ould=20
be physically present (i.e., the Postdoctoral position is not achievable=20
